Note on Railway specifically, since your Dockerfile is written for it: it no longer has a permanent free tier — it's usage-based with a $5/mo Hobby plan minimum now, so I'd point you at Render or Fly.io instead for the free stretch, and only move to Railway once you're paying anyway. 
